{"tid":1355682,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"而家根本啲人連事實都搞錯","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:35:40.000Z","uid":200792,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"421bea261208308792aedcc26c23ace91d7972fd","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"大家唔好因爲自己個圈子入面嘅人醒左，就覺得香港人開始醒。我可以好肯定咁講，而家係<span style=\"color: red;\">好撚多連事實都搞錯</span>。而要呢場運動繼續落去，我地一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">做好文宣</span>。<br />\n<br />\n想講嘅就係元朗單野。唔係講笑，我聽到唔止一個、兩個、三個，唔係小數，係<span style=\"color: red;\">好多人</span>話當晚係黑衫挑釁在先先會俾人打。係，我明，挑釁人唔可以合理化打人，但係嗰啲人真係會信，再blame the victim. 與其嘥時間教佢地咩叫blame the victim，<span style=\"color: red;\">更加直接</span>係要多啲文宣話俾佢聽嗰晚根本冇人挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n更加嚴重嘅係，好多人（包括公司同事）<span style=\"color: red;\">真心相信</span>嗰晚係示威者有光復行動，話係示威者做主動。仲話林卓廷帶隊入去。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，咁撚夜去光復咩？？用常理都諗到啦！而呢個就係個問題所在，好多時我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高估左香港人嘅智商</span></span>，面對何君妖等等嗰啲無理指控只會一笑置之，但係偏偏真係好多人信。<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地一定要做好文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n一定要不斷強調<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白衫見人就打</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警冇阻止</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示威者冇挑釁</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地只係返屋企</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c43937e494de92e4d3e64930d9eb5ef68a5aea2","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbee7b2949dd4143c791c43c81c038824450a0b9","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83876fc5b8197de0aae31e445a1a1935373c3945","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8cad09a2bea052784689a898684323b218d1e","tid":1355682,"uid":136971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421b721744dfbef8ca11d66a98d4f2f576b8ea71","tid":1355682,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩同事都有d智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6736bcb1a20ab530199fa4b5097ea0dd74a46220","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:19:45.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc06562ed96136fa29330bf058d950bead1f984","tid":1355682,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5555f43deda4460590527b93c829b9c8f105e4a3","tid":1355682,"uid":200792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201